story_galar_02_11000/2401_1001_0200_10:
These are the “supporters” Rose was
talking about?!
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1001_0300_10: They’re those troublemakers from Sinnoh, right?
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1001_0400_10: How rude of you to call us troublemakers.
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1001_0500_10:
These days, we believe in science and are working
toward completing the human spirit.
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1001_0600_10:
If Mr. Rose wins, we can expect advancements in
the practical uses of sync stones.
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1001_0700_10:
That would benefit us, which is why we agreed to
this match!
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1001_0800_10:
By no means do we agree with Mr. Rose’s
ideology.
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1001_0900_10:
The only person whose orders we listen to is
Master Cyrus!
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1001_1000_10: And now, we’re going to win this!
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1101_1100_20: The first battle will now begin!
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1001_1200_10:
Go, go, Marnie! Send Team Galactic to the edge
of outer space!
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1001_1300_10:
Maybe I can’t cheer someone on just with the
tunes I play. ♪
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1001_1700_10: Target the one that looks weakest!
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1101_2500_20:
Aaand that settles it! The young Galar team wins
the first battle!
story_galar_02_11000/2401_1001_2800_10:
It seems the connections between hearts have
endless potential after all.
